	(text_box "D5 - SK6805-EC15\n\nAddressable RGB LED with integrated driver\n\nWS2812 / NeoPixel-compatible control protocol\n\nSingle-wire digital data input (DIN)\n\nDOUT for LED chaining\n\nIndividually controllable red, green, and blue channels\n\nPowered from 5 V"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
